	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Proximis tuis literis, d. Bullingere observande, cum responderem, decretum vestrum expectaturos pollicebar<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">Siehe oben <ref target="file11447">Nr. 1404</ref>, 9-11. - Die Rede ist außer von <persName ref="p7092" cert="high">Wolf</persName> selbst auch von <persName ref="p8461" cert="high">Wick</persName> und <persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Haller</persName>.</note>.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Verum, quoniam quasi certissimo<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>korrigiert aus</hi> certissimam.</note> proficiscendi facultatem a vobis datum iri animis nostris conceperamus, non potuimus cum temporis, tum vero maxime itineris quam commodissimam oblatam occasionem praetermittere, ne amissa illa frustra recuperandi tantum non assequendi copia concederetur.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Proinde petitis et comparatis a d. rectore<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="p6943" cert="high">Kaspar Volland</persName>; s. <placeName ref="l512" cert="high">Tübingen</placeName>, Matrikel I 300.</note> et universitat[e] scholae <placeName ref="l512" cert="high">Thubingensis</placeName> [necessari]is[?] testimoniis<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b">[necessari]is testimoniis <hi>am Rande nachgetragen,</hi> im engen Einband nur teilweise lesbar.</note><note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Nicht erhalten.</note><pb type="edition" next="167"/> una cum typographo<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Gemeint ist gewiß der <placeName ref="l512" cert="high">Tübinger</placeName> Buchdrucker <persName ref="p5871" cert="high">Ulrich Morhart</persName>; s. <hi>Benzing,</hi> Buchdrucker 465.</note>, homine piissimo, <placeName ref="l157" cert="high">Francfordiam</placeName> profecti sumus et illinc nunc <placeName ref="l311" cert="high">Marpurgum</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quare te et patronum et patrem seu sacram anchoram<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Vgl. Adagia, 1, 1, 24 (<bibl>LB</bibl> II 35f).</note> oratum quammaxime voluerim, ne id, quod factum est, indignius feras, siquidem totum id factum est, ut aeris alieni obligationem evitaremus, praesertim, quod ob nostri aeris tantam tenuitatem diutius manere non licuisset.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quin iam vale et <persName ref="p7092" cert="high">Wolffium</persName> tuum, quod soles, ama.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l157" cert="high">Francfordię</placeName>, raptim, 1540, 15. septembris.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutabis matrem<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6"><persName ref="p7042" cert="high">Anna, geb. Wiederkehr</persName>.</note>, uxorem<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7"><persName ref="p8051" cert="high">Anna, geb. Adlischwyler</persName>.</note>, liberos<note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8">Siehe oben <ref target="file11387">Nr. 1344</ref>, Anm. 14.</note> etc.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p7092" cert="high">Iohan. Wolffius</persName> tuus quam etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cum docto tum integro viro d. Heinricho Bullingero, Tigurinę ecclesię episcopo vigilantissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
